<br>
I have long been an advocate of forlorn deeds, I still think it's the best spell we get for 6 man groups, maybe the most powerful spell that we get, period.  <br>
<br>
I really think a shaman/bard combo is really good in the absence of an enchanter.  If all the mobs are slowed there's really no excuse to die to any pull.<br>
<br>
Of course this is at 57+ when you get forlorn deeds.. after shaman get torgers(sp) at 51 shiftless deeds can't comppete.<br>
